### [1 Kings (1 Samuel) Chapter 15](../../../bib/kjv/sa1015.htm#001.md)

[1 Kings (1 Samuel)](../../../bib/kjv/sa1001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">sa1 15:0</span></span>

Overview

[Sa1 15:1](../../../bib/kjv/sa1015.htm#001.md), Samuel sends Saul to
destroy Amalek; [Sa1 15:6](../../../bib/kjv/sa1015.htm#006.md), Saul
favours the Kenites; [Sa1 15:7](../../../bib/kjv/sa1015.htm#007.md), He
spares Agag and the best of the spoil; [Sa1
15:10](../../../bib/kjv/sa1015.htm#010.md), Samuel denounces unto Saul
God's rejection of him for his disobedience; [Sa1
15:24](../../../bib/kjv/sa1015.htm#024.md), Saul's humiliation; [Sa1
15:32](../../../bib/kjv/sa1015.htm#032.md), Samuel kills Agag; [Sa1
15:34](../../../bib/kjv/sa1015.htm#034.md), Samuel and Saul part.

